    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Ready to Transform Your Machine?</h2>
        <p>Join the community of coffee enthusiasts building the future of home espresso.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="https://github.com/mizrachiran/brewos" class="btn btn-cta-primary" target="_blank">
